comments: Washington (DAL) contests Murray's (SAC) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Murray (SAC) establishes himself in Exum's (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Sabonis (SAC) is moving alongside Irving's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during Irving's drive.
Sabonis (SAC) places an arm against Exum's (DAL) side as he jumps to contest the driving shot attempt and the resulting contact is marginal.
Gafford (DAL) reaches in and initiates contact with Barnes' (SAC) arm, causing Barnes to lose his balance.
Murray (SAC) establishes himself in Exum's (DAL) path and his legs remain within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
Exum (DAL) attempts to go for the steal and initiates contact with Fox's (SAC) arm, affecting Fox's SQBR
Jones Jr. (DAL) legally contests Barnes's (SAC) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Barnes (SAC) throws the ball from the frontcourt into the backcourt.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Murray (SAC) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Washington (DAL) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Murray's (SAC) arm.
